Also, all of this content is property of Censored.TV. If you put it on YouTube or anywhere else without our permission, we will get it taken down</disclaimer>
    <assets>
      <icon>resources/media/icon.png</icon>
      <fanart>resources/media/fanart.jpg</fanart>
      <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-01.jpg</screenshot>
      <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-02.jpg</screenshot>
      <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-03.jpg</screenshot>
    </assets>
    <language>en</language>
    <platform>all</platform>
    <license>MIT</license>
    <website>https://censored.tv</website>
    <email></email>
    <forum></forum>
    <source>https://github.com/tracey-fans/plugin.video.censoredtv</source>
    <news>
v1.1.2  Updated screenshots &amp; language elements properly supported
